Program: Outlook
Title: The Shopkeeper Defusing IS Booby Traps
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p058bynt
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 19 Jul 2017
Abu Ahmad decided to start work defusing bombs planted by so-called Islamic State in Syria after his nephew was injured by one. American Rita McMahon used to work in television. Now she runs a sanctuary for injured wild birds in New York City. Jack Green is a British athlete who spoke out about how depression affected his career. (Picture credit: Salah Malkawi/Getty Images) Show less